## Project Report

The complete project report documents the design, implementation, testing, and evaluation of the autonomous vehicle.

The report covers the following main topics:

- Background, problem statement, project goals, and constraints
- System design and engineering approach
- System architecture, data flow, and UML diagrams
- Hardware components, electrical connections, and mechanical design
- Software architecture, PID control, and obstacle avoidance
- Simulation, testing, verification, and performance evaluation
- Challenges, current limitations, and future improvements
- Team contributions, conclusion, and lessons learned

